\f0\fs26 \cf0 \cb2 Project Brief - Transportation: The activity I chose to observe was individuals walking to and from class. I chose this activity because I have heard from graduated seniors that walking to classes is a much more enjoyable and fulfilling experience, and I am interested to learn why, and how I can bring these aspects of the experience to other transportation experiences through a mobile application.\'a0\
\
